show.title: Don't Mess With Super Dad

show.description:
When a mild-mannered single dad reveals his hidden powers to protect his daughter, enemies learn the hard way—he’s not just a parent, he’s a powerhouse.
Family comes first, and this Super Dad doesn’t play nice when his child is in danger.
